title: Provided that in the above cited cases of grant of additional FSI for Biotechnology units, premium recovered for the BUA at the rate of 50% of ASR for open develop land (for FSI 1) or as may be determined by Govt
clause_text: Provided that in the above cited cases of grant of additional FSI for Biotechnology units, premium recovered for the BUA at the rate of 50% of ASR for open develop land (for FSI 1) or as may be determined by Govt. shall be paid to MCGM out of which 50% shall be payable to the Govt.
